00:24:34.600 --> 00:24:40.030
punishment system, so that you can punish
the people afterward -- bring them to justice.

00:24:40.030 --> 00:24:47.420
And a prevention system to try to prevent
them from beginning in the first place. Now,

00:24:47.420 --> 00:24:52.100
to the extent that there is serious, that
there are measures being taken today, it's

00:24:52.100 --> 00:24:53.530
in the world of justice.

00:24:53.530 --> 00:25:00.090
There's an international criminal court, but
it is too limited, too slow, too late to be

00:25:00.090 --> 00:25:06.240
a one stop shopping response to the problem
