00:25:06.240 --> 00:25:11.330
talk, there is talk about rapid deployment
forces at the UN and other forms of intervention

00:25:11.330 --> 00:25:17.570
through the UN; there's talk of it. But where
we should really be placing our emphasis is

00:25:17.570 --> 00:25:21.940
on prevention for the obvious reason that
we don't want these things to begin in the

00:25:21.940 --> 00:25:29.000
first place. Keep in mind that in a day, the
