00:25:45.560 --> 00:25:50.160
And what do you do with the perpetrators?
How do you get them to stop when they've already

00:25:50.160 --> 00:25:57.240
thrown their lot in with this kind of policy?
And so, and another reason we should focus

00:25:57.240 --> 00:26:04.260
