00:27:31.600 --> 00:27:36.870
The leaders of these militaries don't want
their capacities to be destroyed. In Bosnia,

00:27:36.870 --> 00:27:42.420
when we finally began to bomb seriously, we
being NATO, in 1995, after the massacre in

00:27:42.420 --> 00:27:48.520
